The remaining costs includeÂ 25% of the MBS fee for doctors' services and any
amount the doctors charge above the MBS fee, plus some or all the costs of:

* hospital accommodation;
* theatre fees;
* intensive care;Â
* drugs, dressings and other consumables;
* prostheses (surgically implanted);
* diagnostic tests;
* pharmaceuticals; and
* any additional doctor's fees.

